Task Name:ContactUtils

Duration:  4 to 6hrs

Description:
1.) In home screen, Read the user contacts from phone and display in the list
2.) Each contact item has a select option(tick) to store the contact number in locally
3.) Whenever you get a call from the selected contact number we need to display the below popup with name, number(no need profile picture).
4.) If you un select the number popup don't need to display.

Follow:

Android
MVVM Or MVP
Shared Preference
